OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777821065
OL,3,C'Stay away from area' warning as WW2
OL,4,Cbomb to be blown up where it was found
OL,6,FPeople are being told to stay away
OL,7,Ffrom the Southway area of Plymouth, as
OL,8,Fexperts prepare to detonate a 250kg
OL,9,FSecond World War bomb found on a
OL,10,Fconstruction site.
OL,12,FThey say the device isn't safe to
OL,13,Fmove, so it must be blown up in situ.
OL,15,FSpecialist teams have been building a
OL,16,Fmitigation structure on Flamborough
OL,17,FRoad overnight (Friday, 1 May) to
OL,18,Flimit the impact of the controlled
OL,19,Fexplosion, using large quantities of
OL,20,Fsand.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
