FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777821065
OL,3,C'Stay away from area' warning as WW2
OL,4,Cbomb to be blown up where it was found
OL,6,FRoyal Navy and Army UXO specialists
OL,7,Fhave completed a rigorous and detailed
OL,8,Fassessment of the device. The time of
OL,9,Fdetonation hasn't been confirmed, but
OL,10,Fit will only happen once all safety
OL,11,Fmeasures are fully in place.
OL,13,FPlymouth City Council is warning
OL,14,Fpeople to stay away from the area.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777821065
OL,3,C'Stay away from area' warning as WW2
OL,4,Cbomb to be blown up where it was found
OL,6,FIn a statement, it said: "You will not
OL,7,Fbe able to see this 'detonation' from
OL,8,Fany point around the cordon, so please
OL,9,Fstay away from the area. The Police
OL,10,Fhave also issued a no-fly zone over
OL,11,Fthe site, which means no drones are
OL,12,Fallowed."
OL,14,FWork to reduce the impact is ongoing,
OL,15,Fand thousands of residents have spent
OL,16,Fa second night away from home after
OL,17,Fauthorities evacuated properties
OL,18,Fwithin a 400 metre cordon on
OL,19,FWednesday, 29 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777821065
OL,3,C'Stay away from area' warning as WW2
OL,4,Cbomb to be blown up where it was found
OL,6,FRemoval of the cordon and returning
OL,7,Fhome
OL,9,FOnce the device has been made safe and
OL,10,Fspecialists have given the green
OL,11,Flight, the council will announce on
OL,12,Fits website and on social media when
OL,13,Fthe cordon will be lifted.
OL,15,FPlymouth City Council added: "The
OL,16,Fevacuation is essential so specialists
OL,17,Fcan proceed safely with the next stage
OL,18,Fof work. This is about protecting
OL,19,Flives, including your own and those of
OL,20,Fyour neighbours.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
