OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777821065
OL,3,C'Stay away from area' warning as WW2
OL,4,Cbomb to be blown up where it was found
OL,6,F"If you can, please make arrangements
OL,7,Fto stay with friends or family. If you
OL,8,Fcannot do this, support is available.
OL,10,F"If you are leaving your home,
OL,11,Fremember to leave your windows open,
OL,12,Fturn off your water supply and take
OL,13,Fessential items with you for the next
OL,14,Fcouple of days."
OL,16,FAccommodation and evacuation centre
OL,17,Fsupport
OL,19,FFor residents already placed in
OL,20,Ftemporary accommodation, bookings will
OL,21,Fbe automatically extended.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
