PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777821065
OL,3,C'Stay away from area' warning as WW2
OL,4,Cbomb to be blown up where it was found
OL,6,FAn evacuation centre at Southway Youth
OL,7,Fand Community Centre remains open, and
OL,8,Fofficers will be there to provide
OL,9,Fadvice, support and help with
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FSchool closures
OL,14,FOakwood Primary School, Little Acorns
OL,15,FPreSchool and Beechwood Primary
OL,16,FSchool remain shut.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
